# Preseed assets for SilverBullet copied into /opt/silverbullet-preseed/ at
# build time (Dockerfile) and into /home/user/.obsidian_vault/.silverbullet/
# at first session boot (entrypoint.sh).
#
# - config.yaml         Always present. Auth-less SB config.
# - atlas.plug.js       Best-effort. If Atlas plug binary is available at
#                       implementation time, drop here and entrypoint will
#                       install it. If absent, vault visualisation falls back
#                       to graphify-out/graph.html (always available).
